{
  "page_title": "第三方应用开发 - 服务端API",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "编辑文档内容",
      "api_name": "batch_update",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/wedoc/document/batch_update",
      "description": "该接口可以对一个在线文档批量执行多个更新操作。",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "访问令牌"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "docid",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "文档的docid"
        },
        {
          "name": "version",
          "type": "uint32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "操作的文档版本, 该参数可以通过获取文档内容接口获得。操作后文档版本将更新一版。要更新的文档版本与最新文档版本相差不能超过100个。"
        },
        {
          "name": "requests",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": true,
          "description": "更新操作列表"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "错误码说明"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "请求示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"docid\": \"DOCID\",\n\t\"verison\": 10,\n\t\"requests\": [\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"insert_text\": {\n\t\t\t\t\"text\": \"text content\",\n\t\t\t\t\"location\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t\"index\": 10\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"insert_table\": {\n\t\t\t\t\"rows\": 2,\n\t\t\t\t\"cols\": 2,\n\t\t\t\t\"location\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t\"index\": 10\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "返回示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"errcode\": 0,\n\t\"errmsg\": \"ok\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": []
    },
    {
      "group_title": "参数详细说明",
      "api_name": "UpdateRequest",
      "method": "",
      "api_url": "",
      "description": "更新文档的操作，每个UpdateRequest的Object中能同时填一个字段，填入多个的只会有一个生效",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "访问令牌"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [],
      "response_params": [],
      "request_examples": [],
      "response_examples": [],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "字段说明",
          "content": "| 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| replace_text | object(ReplaceText) | 替换指定位置文本内容 |\n| insert_text | object(InsertText) | 在指定位置插入文本内容 |\n| delete_content | object(DeleteContent) | 删除指定位置内容 |\n| insert_image | object(InsertImage) | 在指定位置插入图片 |\n| insert_page_break | object(InsertPageBreak) | 在指定位置插入分页符 |\n| insert_table | object(InsertTable) | 在指定位置插入表格 |\n| insert_paragraph | object(InsertParagraph) | 在指定位置插入段落 |\n| update_text_property | object(UpdateTextProperty) | 更新指定位置文本属性 |"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
